# Runtime data now lives in Supabase (USE_SUPABASE=true). These JSON stores
# are the local-dev fallback only and can contain scraped lead/company data,
# so keep them out of git. The static seed datasets + config are re-included
# below (the seeder needs airports/populated-places to bootstrap a fresh box).
data/*
!data/airports.json
!data/populated-places.json
!data/icps.json
!data/email-templates.json
# scrape-cache/ is a subdir under data/ - covered by `data/*`, stays ignored.